'''Mpho Osei Tutu''' (yavutse ku ya 31 Ukuboza 1981), ni umukinnyi wa firime  w’umufaransa wavukiye [[Afurika y’Epfo|muri Afurika yepfo]] akaba numuhanzi wijwi ukomoka muri Gana-Mosotho. <ref name="tvsa">https://www.tvsa.co.za/actors/viewactor.aspx?actorid=7354</ref> Azwi cyane kubera uruhare rwe muri firime na seri za tereviziyo:Seriously single,''Mrs Right Guy'' and ''The Jakes Are Missing'' .  Uretse gukora, kandi ni screenwriter, umuyobozi na producer. Tutu kandi yakinnye nk'umuntu wambere  muri serie yo muri Afrika yepfo 2018 yitwa '''The Imposter''' yari iyerekwa ryumuhungu wa kabiri nyuma yicyerekezo cyumukobwa wa mbere, yakinnye nka Tebogo na Gary Mokoena.

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 31 Ukuboza 1981 i [[Paris|Paris mu]] [[Ubufaransa|Bufaransa]] kwa se o muri Gana na nyina uva muri Mosotho. Kubera inkomoko y’amahanga, yabayeho mu bihugu byinshi: Lesotho, Ubufaransa, Ubwongereza, Togo na Gana. Mu 1992, umuryango we watuye muri Afurika y'Epfo. Yatangiye ikinamico afite imyaka umunani. Nyuma yaje kubona impamyabumenyi ya BA (Hons) muri Dramatic Art yakuye muri kaminuza ya Wits . 

Yashakanye na Tumi Morake, umukinnyi wa filime mugenzi we, umunyarwenya n'umwanditsi. <ref>https://www.afropolitan.co.za/articles/tumi-morake-mpho-osei-tutu-10697.html</ref> Bashakanye ku ya 28 Ugushyingo 2009. <ref>https://www.bona.co.za/tumi-morake-and-mpho-osei-tutu-celebrate-their-10th-anniversary/</ref> Abashakanye bafite abana batatu. <ref>http://www.channel24.co.za/The-Juice/News/tumi-morake-and-mpho-osie-tutu-celebrate-their-10-year-anniversary-20191128</ref> <ref>https://www.dispatchlive.co.za/lifestyle/entertainment/2019-11-29-tumi-morake-and-hubby-mpho-osie-tutu-celebrate-their-anniversary/</ref> <ref>https://www.timeslive.co.za/tshisa-live/tshisa-live/2018-01-10-my-kids-are-traumatised-but-i-thank-god-everyday-were-safe-tumi-morake/</ref> <ref>http://www.bona.co.za/tumi-morake-mpho-osei-tutu-celebrate-8th-anniversary/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Yatangiye gukina mu ikinamico aho yakinnye inshuro nyinshi mu gukina amakinamico ya Zakes Mda ya''The Mother Of All Eating'', Pieter-Dirk Uys 'MacBeki, Paul Slabolepsky ''For Your Ears Only'', ''The Island'' . Hamwe naba nyuma, yazengurutse Ubwongereza, Amerika n'Ubugereki. Noneho yakoze ''Getting On'' Yatsindiye Igihembo Cyiza Muri rusange Gucibwa muri Multi Choice VUKA! Ibihembo muri 2006. Nyuma yakinnye abantu benshi mumashusho ye yise ''Carvincing Carlos'' aho yakiriye igihembo cyambere cya Bank  Ovation Award muri 2010. Ku ruhare 'La Fleche' mu ikinamico ya Sylvaine Strike ''The Miser'' yatsindiye Umukino mwiza muri Naledi Theatre Awards 2013 . 

Hagati aho, yinjiye kuri tereviziyo, akina muri sitcoms nyinshi ''Kota Life Crisis'', ''High Rollers'', ''Samsokolo'' ; kubyo yatorewe kuba umukinnyi mwiza muri TV Comedy muri SAFTAs 2014. Hanyuma yakinnye nka 'Desmond' muri International Emmy Nominated serial ''Home Home'' . Hanyuma yerekanye uruhare rwa 'Bomba' muri firime yamamaye ku rwego mpuzamahanga ''A Million Colors'' . Yatowe kandi nk'umukinnyi witwaye neza muri Filime Yerekana muri SAFTAs 2013 kuri iyi film. Ni n'umuhanzi uzwi cyane aho yavugiye amajwi kuri radiyo nyinshi. <ref name="tvsa" />

Usibye gukina, ''yanakoze nk'umwanditsi wa sinema Ses Top La'', ''Tempy Pushas'', ''My Perfect Family'' aho yatoranije kwandika neza muri Comedy ya TV muri SAFTAs 2014, ndetse na ''Rhythm City'' yatsindiye igihembo cyiza Yandika mu ikinamico  ya TV muri SAFTAs mu 2009., Mu 2010, yanditse ''Hopeville'' kandi atoranyirizwa igihembo mpuzamahanga cya Emmy mu 2010. Hagati aho, yanabaye umuyobozi w''<nowiki/>'amafilime nka Zone 14'', ''Ga Re Dumele 4'' na ''Kota Life Crisis'' . <ref name="tvsa" />

Nyuma yaje gukorana na firime ngufi ''Joburg'' yatoranijwe kumugaragaro muri Sundance Film Festival mu 2010. Yashinze isosiyete ikora firime, 'What Not Entertainment' nyuma akora ibihe 2 bya sitcom ''Kota Life Crisis'' ya Mzansi Magic. Kuva mu 2012 kugeza 2014, yakoraga mu buyobozi bw'Ishyirahamwe ry'Abakinnyi bo muri Afurika y'Epfo (SAGA). Hagati aho, niwe wateguye ishyirahamwe ryitwa Repertory Amateur Players Society (RAPS) One Act Plays Festival, ifatwa nkumunsi mukuru wo gukina amakinamico maremare kandi yamamaye muri Afrika yepfo. <ref name="tvsa" />

Muri Kanama 2020, yakinnye muri filime yo gusetsa igitsina ''Seriously Single'' afatanije na Katleho Ramaphakela na Rethabile Ramaphakela. <ref>https://www.news24.com/drum/celebs/news/seriously-singles-bohang-moeko-and-yonda-thomas-reflect-on-love-and-dating-20200817</ref> Yasohotse ku ya 31 Nyakanga 2020 kuri Netflix . <ref>http://myheraldmagazine.com/seriously-single-romantic-comedy-premieres-on-netflix-on-31st-july-2020/</ref>

